Class BuildInformation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opends.quicksetup.BuildInformation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<BuildInformation>

    public class BuildInformation
extends Object
implements Comparable<BuildInformation>
    Represents information about the current build that is publicly obtainable by invoking start-ds -F.

        public static BuildInformation create(Installation installation)

        Reads build information for a particular installation by reading the output from invoking the start-ds tool with the full information option.
        Parameters:
        installation - from which to gather build information
        Returns:
        BuildInformation object populated with information
        Throws:
        ApplicationException - if all or some important information could not be determined

      • fromBuildString

        public static BuildInformation fromBuildString(String bn)
                                        throws IllegalArgumentException
        Creates an instance from a string representing a build number of the for MAJOR.MINOR.POINT.REVISION where MAJOR, MINOR, POINT, and REVISION are integers.
        Parameters:
        bn - String representation of a build number
        Returns:
        a BuildInformation object populated with the information provided in bn
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if bn is not a build number
